    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Art Spotting Co-op is a casual game about spotting the difference between several art pieces together with a friend while listening to relaxing music. A controller is not required for local co-op play.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 players will work together to spot the differences between left and right art on the screen. Player 1 will control the cursor using the mouse and player 2 will control another cursor using the keyboard. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual, simple and relaxing game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several beautiful western, eastern and modern art pieces</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All art pieces are family-friendly</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each art is accompanied with their own music</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-player local co-op using only a mouse and a keyboard (no controller required)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Autosaves and autoloads</p></li></ul>",
